---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Docs — logic2b/ui">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Introduction</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
      logic2b ui is a set of copy-paste React + Tailwind components with a
      shadcn-compatible registry. Full documentation is under construction
      (Phase 2). The registry is already live:
      <a href="/r/index.json" class="text-foreground underline underline-offset-4"
        >/r/index.json</a
      >
      — e.g.
      <a href="/r/button.json" class="text-foreground underline underline-offset-4"
        >/r/button.json</a
      >.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
